{"published time": "2024-03-11T15-33-43-03-00", "images": ["https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/protestos-morte-chico-mendes-florianopolis-sao-jose-696x408-1.webp"], "content": "<div class=\"el-single-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/protestos-morte-chico-mendes-florianopolis-sao-jose-696x408-1.webp\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/protestos-morte-chico-mendes-florianopolis-sao-jose-696x408-1.webp 696w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/protestos-morte-chico-mendes-florianopolis-sao-jose-696x408-1-300x176.webp 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/protestos-morte-chico-mendes-florianopolis-sao-jose-696x408-1-60x35.webp 60w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"408\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/protestos-morte-chico-mendes-florianopolis-sao-jose-696x408-1.webp\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/protestos-morte-chico-mendes-florianopolis-sao-jose-696x408-1.webp\" width=\"696\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n <p>\n  Los residentes de diferentes barrios marginales en el vecindario de Monte Cristo cerraron diferentes caminos en una protesta durante el 9 de marzo, organizados despu\u00e9s del asesinato, dos d\u00edas antes, de un joven en la favela de Grota por agentes de polic\u00eda civil de la coordinaci\u00f3n de recursos especiales (Core). Los residentes afirman que el joven estaba desarmado.\n </p>\n <p>\n  La protesta concentr\u00f3 a los residentes de las favelas de Grota, Chico Mendes, Sap\u00e9 y otras comunidades. Los videos registran enormes barricadas de fuego en caminos importantes en la regi\u00f3n, como Josu\u00e9 Di Bernardi Avenue, Joaquim Nabuco y Jos\u00e9 Antonio Tonolli. La revuelta popular en la condena de las redadas policiales y los asesinatos en las comunidades comenz\u00f3 en la tarde del 03/03 y continu\u00f3 hasta los amanecer del 10/03.\n </p>\n <blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/C4T2I1sA6oC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"14\" style=\" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);\">\n  <div style=\"padding:16px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/C4T2I1sA6oC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\" background:#FFFFFF; line-height:0; padding:0 0; text-align:center; text-decoration:none; width:100%;\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <div style=\" display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;\">\n     <div style=\"background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;\">\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;\">\n      <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;\">\n      </div>\n      <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;\">\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding: 19% 0;\">\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;\">\n     <svg height=\"50px\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 60 60\" width=\"50px\" xmlns=\"https://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\">\n      <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\">\n       <g fill=\"#000000\" transform=\"translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)\">\n        